ehicles%20swallowed%20by%20the%20gushing%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20the%20worst%20hit%20with%20the%20torrential%20rains%20turning%20roads%20to%20rivers%20and%20rivers%20to%20angry%20seas%20washing%20away%20everything%20on%20its%20path%20-%20cars%2C%20houses%2C%20or%20bridges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20count%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20has%20gone%20up%20to%2031%2C%20while%20the%20neighbouring%20Uttarakhand%20has%20reported%20five%20rain-related%20deaths%2C%20while%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Rajasthan%20reported%20one%20death%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20conducted%20an%20aerial%20survey%20on%20Tuesday%20of%20the%20Kasol%2C%20Manikaran%2C%20Kheer%20Ganga%2C%20and%20Pulga%20areas.%20In%20Kull's%20Sainj%20area%20alone%2C%20around%2040%20shops%20and%2030%20houses%20were%20washed%20away%2C%20he%20said%2C%20as%20he%20interacted%20with%20people%20in%20a%20relied%20camp%20in%20Kullu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20loss%20of%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20state%20is%20estimated%20at%20between%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20and%20Rs.%204%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20have%20been%20receiving%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20to%20extremely%20heavy%26quot%3B%20rainfall%20over%20the%20last%20four%20days.%20This%20has%20flooded%20rivers%2C%20creeks%2C%20and%20drains%2C%20which%20has%20massively%20damaged%20infrastructure%20and%20disrupted%20essential%20services%20in%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20department%20has%20issued%20a%20red%20alert%20for%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20three%20districts%20in%20Uttarakhand%20today.%20Uttarakhand%20authorities%20have%20urged%20people%20to%20not%20travel%20to%20the%20state%20till%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20the%20Yamuna%20river%20has%20risen%20to%20the%20highest%20recorded%20level%20in%2010%20years%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20rise%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Central%20Water%20Commission's%20(CWC)%20flood-monitoring%20portal%2C%20the%20water%20level%20at%20the%20Old%20Railway%20Bridge%20in%20New%20Delhi%20crossed%20207%20metres%20at%205%20am%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20increase%20in%20water%20level%20is%20a%20result%20of%20Haryana%20releasing%20more%20water%20into%20the%20river%20from%20the%20Hathnikund%20barrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20recorded%20a%20rapid%20increase%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20water%20level%20over%20the%20last%20two%20days.%20It%20shot%20up%20from%20203.14%20metres%20at%2011%20am%20on%20Sunday%20to%20205.4%20at%205%20pm%20on%20Monday%2C%20breaching%20the%20danger%20mark%20of%20205.33%20metres%2018%20hours%20earlier%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESixteen%20control%20rooms%20have%20been%20set%20up%20to%20monitor%20the%20flood-prone%20areas%20and%20the%20water%20level%20of%20the%20Yamuna.%20More%20than%2050%20motorboats%20have%20been%20deployed%20for%20rescue-and-relief%20operations%2C%20and%20diving%20and%20medical%20teams%20have%20been%20readied%20with%20all%20the%20necessary%20materials%20and%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689131400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fjgisavig_himachal-rain_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frain-fury-continues-across-north-india-yamuna-water-levels-at-10-year-high-4199083%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rains%20for%20a%20fourth%20consecutive%20day%20led%20to%20several%20deaths%2C%20landslides%2C%20and%20destruction%20across%20North%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frain-fury-continues-across-north-india-yamuna-water-levels-at-10-year-high-4199083%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frain-fury-continues-across-north-india-yamuna-water-levels-at-10-year-high-4199083%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frain-fury-continues-across-north-india-yamuna-water-levels-at-10-year-high-4199083%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Sweeps%20Violence-Hit%20Bengal%20Rural%20Polls%2C%20BJP%20Gains%20But%20Distant%202nd%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20swept%20the%20West%20Bengal%20panchayat%20elections%2C%20winning%20a%20majority%20in%20all%20three%20tiers%20of%20the%20rural%20local%20government.%20The%20TMC%20won%202%2C552%20out%20of%203%2C317%20gram%20panchayats%2C%20232%20panchayat%20samitis%2C%20and%2012%20out%20of%2020%20zilla%20parishads.%20The%20BJP%20was%20a%20distant%20second%2C%20winning%20only%20212%20gram%20panchayats%2C%207%20panchayat%20samitis%2C%20and%20no%20zilla%20parishads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20results%20are%20still%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20TMC%20all%20the%20way%20in%20rural%20Bengal.%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20people%20for%20their%20love%2C%20affection%20and%20support%20towards%20the%20TMC.%20This%20election%20has%20proved%20that%20only%20TMC%20resides%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counting%20of%20votes%20for%20the%20panchayat%20elections%20began%20yesterday%20morning.%20Over%2074%2C000%20seats%20are%20up%20for%20grabs%2C%20including%2063%2C229%20gram%20panchayat%20seats%2C%209%2C730%20panchayat%20samiti%20seats%2C%20and%20928%20zilla%20parishad%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polls%2C%20billed%20as%20a%20test%20of%20popularity%20for%20Trinamool%20supremo%20and%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20saw%20rampant%20violence%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20repolling%20on%20Monday%20was%20agai