tizens%20must%20first%20apply%20for%20a%20licence%20and%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Flaw%2Fgun-license-rules-india-arms-act-arms-rules-personal-protection-types-of-weapons-over-21%23read-more%2523read-more%5C%22%3Eseveral%20rules%20and%20regulations%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20govern%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20former%20Manipur%20police%20commissioner%20Raj%20Kumar%20Nimai%20raised%20a%20concern%20surrounding%20the%20data.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20figure%20of%208%2C000%20weapons%20%5Blicences%5D%20issued%20in%20just%20five%20years%20is%20quite%20staggering%2C%20and%20%5Bdistrict%20collectors%20or%20magistrates%5D%20can%E2%80%99t%20issue%20weapons%20in%20such%20capacity%20without%20letting%20the%20state%20know.%20If%20this%20has%20happened%2C%20then%20there%20must%20have%20been%20pressure%20on%20the%20collectors%20from%20the%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20is%20not%20very%20keen%2C%20then%20no%20collector%20will%20issue%20licences%20at%20that%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20DGP%20of%20Assam%20G.M.%20Srivastava%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20weapons%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20licensed%2C%20there%20must%20have%20been%20a%20supply%20from%20China%20and%20Myanmar.%20Not%20from%20the%20Myanmar%20government%20but%20from%20a%20group%20in%20Myanmar%3B%20China%20has%20an%20interest%20in%20Northeast%20not%20from%20now%20but%20from%201947.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConcerns%20about%20gun%20ownership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20also%20holds%20the%20portfolio%20of%20home%20in%20the%20state%2C%20to%20whom%20district%20collectors%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Budget%20Session%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feasternmirrornagaland.com%2Fre-poll-in-four-polling-stations%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20around%20%E2%80%9C10%20violent%20cases%20including%20human%20casualties%20using%20licensed%20guns%E2%80%9D%20were%20reported%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20past%20two%20or%20three%20years.%20He%20was%20responding%20to%20Kuki%20MLAs%20Vungzagin%20Valte%20and%20Paolienlal%20Haokip%20about%20the%20Churachandpur%20district%20magistrate%20asking%20people%20to%20submit%20arms%20licences%20along%20with%20the%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLAs%20were%20insinuating%20that%20the%20scrutiny%20was%20underway%20only%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20a%20Kuki-majority%20district%2C%20but%20Singh%20claimed%20later%20that%20the%20process%20was%20initiated%20across%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20has%20launched%20these%20measures%20to%20curb%20and%20prevent%20incidents%20of%20gun-related%20violence%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20prevails%20in%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20district%20magistrates%20and%20superintendents%20of%20police%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexamine%20the%20purpose%20carefully%20before%20issuing%20an%20arms%20license%E2%80%9D%20and%20asked%20arms%20license%20holders%20to%20renew%20their%20licenses%2C%20or%20their%20arms%20would%20be%20considered%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20began%2C%20drop%20boxes%20have%20been%20installed%20in%20several%20places%20for%20people%20to%20return%20weapons%20and%20ammunition%20that%20were%20looted%20or%20snatched%20from%20police%20stations.%20Minister%20L.%20Susindro%20Meitei%2C%20has%20installed%20a%20drop%20box%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Khurai%2C%20Imphal%20East%2C%20inviting%20people%20to%20return%20stolen%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1