chargesheet%20filed%20against%20him%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%20Asked%20the%20question%20by%20Times%20Now%2C%20the%20six-time%20MP%20not%20only%20refused%2C%20but%20also%20misbehaved%20with%20the%20reporter%20and%20slammed%20a%20car%20door%20on%20the%20mic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20filed%20a%201000-page%20chargesheet%20against%20the%20Federation%20chief%20after%20detailed%20investigation%20that%20included%20questioning%20over%20100%20people.%20Sources%20said%2015%20of%20those%20questioned%20testified%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20seven%20wrestlers%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%20Among%20them%20were%20the%20wrestlers'%20friends%20and%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20stalking%2C%20wrongful%20confinement%20and%20criminal%20intimidation.%20A%20second%20FIR%20(First%20Information%20Report)%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20him%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20allegations%20by%20a%20minor%20wrestler%2C%20which%20was%20registered%20under%20POCSO%20(Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences)%20Act.%20He%20faces%20three%20and%20seven%20years%20in%20jail%20under%20the%20two%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20police%2C%20though%2C%20have%20requested%20a%20cancellation%20of%20the%20POCSO%20case%2C%20citing%20lack%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20Rouse%20Avenue%20Court%20has%20summoned%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20chief%20on%20July%2018.%20%26quot%3BThe%20evidence%20is%20enough%20to%20try%20and%20punish%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20asked%20about%20the%20charges%20against%20him%2C%20which%20allege%20repeated%20and%20continuous%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20chief%20said%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bspeak%20in%20court%26quot%3B%20and%20refused%20to%20give%20any%20%26quot%3Bmasala%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Singh%20had%20denied%20all%20allegations%20and%20said%20he%20would%20step%20down%20only%20if%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20wants%20him%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wrestlers%20--%20many%20of%20them%20national%20and%20international%20medal%20winners%20--%20had%20held%20a%20protest%20demanding%20action%20against%20him%20earlier%20this%20year.%20In%20April%2C%20they%20hit%20the%20streets%2C%20holding%20a%20sit-in%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20till%20they%20were%20evicted%20after%20several%20run-ins%20with%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20of%20Olympians%20being%20pinned%20to%20the%20road%20and%20dragged%20off%20by%20the%20police%20had%20triggered%20shock%20and%20outrage%20across%20the%20nation.%20Shortly%20after%2C%20the%20government%20stepped%20in%2C%20asking%20the%20wrestlers%20to%20wait%20till%20the%20police%20finished%20their%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689104220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F72b9nkn_brij-bhushan-sharan-singh_625x300_31_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faccused-of-molestation-stalking-wrestling-chief-says-wont-step-down-4198359%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20the%20benched%20chief%20of%20the%20country's%20Wrestling%20Federation%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20has%20refused%20to%20step%20down%20despite%20the%20chargesheet%20filed%20against%20him%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faccused-of-molestation-stalking-wrestling-chief-says-wont-step-down-4198359%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faccused-of-molestation-stalking-wrestling-chief-says-wont-step-down-4198359%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faccused-of-molestation-stalking-wrestling-chief-says-wont-step-down-419