098338000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F575C%2Fproduction%2F_130346322_mediaitem130346318.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66162502%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20suspect%20has%20been%20arrested%20after%20Stanislav%20Rzhitsky%20was%20gunned%20down%20in%20the%20Russian%20city%20of%20Krasnodar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A925%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66162502%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66162502.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66162502.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2228%25%20GST%20Decision%20%5C%22Will%20Wipe%20Out%20Entire%20Industry%5C%22%3A%20Online%20Gaming%20Firms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOnline%20gaming%20companies%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20levying%20of%2028%20per%20cent%20GST%20will%20limit%20their%20ability%20to%20invest%20in%20new%20games%2C%20impact%20cash%20flows%20as%20well%20as%20business%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GST%20Council%20has%20agreed%20to%20impose%20a%2028%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20online%20gaming%2C%20casinos%20and%20horse%20racing.%20The%20tax%20would%20be%20levied%20on%20the%20full%20face%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20All%20India%20Gaming%20Federation%20(AIGF)%2C%20which%20represents%20companies%20like%20Nazara%2C%20GamesKraft%2C%20Zupee%20and%20Winzo%2C%20said%20the%20decision%20by%20the%20council%20is%20unconstitutional%2C%20irrational%2C%20and%20egregious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20ignores%20over%2060%20years%20of%20settled%20legal%20jurisprudence%20and%20lumps%20online%20skill%20gaming%20with%20gambling%20activities.%20This%20decision%20will%20wipe%20out%20the%20entire%20Indian%20gaming%20industry%20and%20lead%20to%20lakhs%20of%20job%20losses%20and%20the%20only%20people%20benefitting%20from%20this%20will%20be%20anti-national%20illegal%20offshore%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20AIGF%20CEO%20Roland%20Landers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20when%20the%20central%20government%20has%20been%20supporting%20the%20industry%2C%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20such%20a%20legally%20untenable%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%2C%20ignoring%20the%20views%20of%20most%20GoM%20states%20who%20studied%20this%20matter%20in%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnline%20gaming%20players%20have%20repeatedly%20urged%20the%20government%20and%20the%20GST%20Council%20to%20levy%2018%20per%20cent%20GST%20on%20their%20segment%20instead%20of%2028%20per%20cent%20that%20was%20recommended%20by%20Group%20of%20Ministers%20(GoM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20implementation%20of%20a%2028%20per%20cent%20tax%20rate%20will%20bring%20significant%20challenges%20to%20the%20gaming%20industry.%20This%20higher%20tax%20burden%20will%20impact%20companies'%20cash%20flows%2C%20limiting%20their%20ability%20to%20invest%20in%20innovation%2C%20research%2C%20and%20business%20expansion%2C%26quot%3B%20IndiaPlays%20COO%20Aaditya%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20skill-based%20games%20and%20apps%20engaged%20in%20betting%20or%20casinos%20should%20not%20be%20treated%20in%20the%20same%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE-Gaming%20Federation%20(EGF)%2C%20whose%20members%20include%20Games%2024x7%20and%20Junglee%20Games%2C%20said%20that%20a%20tax%20burden%20where%20taxes%20exceed%20revenues%20will%20not%20only%20make%20the%20online%20gaming%20industry%20unviable%20but%20also%20boost%20black%20market%20operators%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20legitimate%20tax-paying%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20employment%20opportunities%20and%20the%20huge%20impact%20on%20marquee%20investors%20who%20are%20heavily%20invested%20in%20this%20sunrise%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20EGF%20Secretary%20Kumar%20Shukla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEGF%20claimed%20that%20online%20gaming%20is%20different%20from%20gambling%2C%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20various%20High%20Court%20decisions%20have%20reaffirmed%20the%20status%20of%20online%20skill-based%20games%20as%20legitimate%20business%20activity%20protected%20as%20a%20fundamental%20right%20under%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20industry%20was%20quite%20optimistic%20with%20the%20new%20developments%20including%20amendments%20to%20the%20IT%20rules%20and%20implementation%20of%20TDS%20on%20net%20winnings%2C%20all%20this%20will%20be%20moot%20if%20the%20industry%20is%20not%20supported%20by%20a%20progressive%20GST%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20Shukla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRIP%20-%20Real%20money%20gaming%20industry%20in%20India.%20If%20the%20govt%20is%20thinking%20people%20will%20put%20in%20Rs%20100%20to%20play%20on%20Rs%2072%20pot%20entry%20(28%20per%20cent%20gross%20GST)%3B%20and%20if%20they%20win%20Rs%2054%20(after%20platform%20fees)-%20they%20will%20pay%2030%20per%20cent%20TDS%20on%20that%20-%20for%20which%20they%20will%20get%20free%20swimming%20pool%20in%20their%20living%20room%20come%20the%20first%20monsoon%20-%20not%20happening%20!%26quot%3B%20Grover%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20is%20time%20for%20startup%20founders%20to%20enter%20politics%20and%20be%20represented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20good%20fun%20being%20part%20of%20the%20fantasy%20gaming%20industry%20-%20which%20stands%20murdered%20now.%20USD%2010%20billion%20down%20the%20drain%20in%20this%20monsoon%2C%26quot%3B%20Gorver%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayerzPot%20Co-Founder%20%26amp%3B%20Director%20Mitesh%20Gangar%20said%20the%20higher%20burden%20will%20also%20impact%20the%20country's%20massive%20gaming%20industry%20and%20deter%20new%20players%20from%20entering%20the%20industry.%20%26quot%3BThe%20rising%20gaming%20economy%20will%20take%20a%20big%20hit%20and%20trigger%20economic%20stress%2C%20restrict%20job%20creation%20and%20curtail%20economic%20growth%20within%20the%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20Gangar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFederation%20of%20Indian%20Fantasy%20Sports%20(FIFS)%20said%20the%20decision%20will%20shift%20users%20to%20illegal%20betting%20platforms%20leading%20to%20user%20risk%20and%20loss%20of%20revenue%20for%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeloitte%20India%2C%20Partner%2C%20Shilpy%20Chaturvedi%20said%20the%20council%20has%20proposed%20to%20increase%20the%20tax%20rate%20to%2028%20per%20cent%20rate%20and%20that%20too%20on%20the%20entry%20amount%20particularly%20for%20real%20money%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoreover%2C%20the%20GST%20Council%20has%20recommended%20to%20remove%20the%20critical%20distinction%20between%20game%20of%20skill%20and%20game%20of%20chance%2C%20which%20has%20always%20been%20a%20determining%20factor%20in%20applying%20rate%20of%20tax%20and%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20distinction%20had%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20challenge%2C%20not%20only%20for%20the%20GST%20but%20under%20regulatory%20laws%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Chaturvedi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20that%20the%20distinction%20between%20games%20of%20skill%20and%20chance%20has%20been%20done%20away%20with.%20This%20is%20a%20setback%20for%20Indian%20gaming%20industry%20as%20they%20were%20expecting%20that%20at%20least%20the%20levy%20will%20be%20on%20the%20margin%20and%20not%20on%20full%20face%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20Shardul%20Amarchand%20Mangaldas%20and%20Co%20Partner%20Rajat%20Bose%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaxmann%2C%20Lead%2C%20Indirect%20Tax%2C%20Kishore%20Kumar%2C%20said%20the%20blanket%20proposal%20to%20levy%20GST%20on%20full%20face%20value%20on%20online%20gaming%20will%20possibly%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20sub-judice%20debate%20of%20'game%20of%20skill'%20versus%20'game%20of%20chance'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20change%20will%20bring%20the%20game%20of%20skill%20at%20par%20with%20wagering%20contracts%20which%20are%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20gamb