nd%20ethnicities%E2%80%9D%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D314%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252F100094123640266%252Fvideos%252F844436120739529%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D560%26t%3D4915%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSA%20said%20that%20India%20is%20an%20inclusive%20democracy%20which%20has%20provided%20space%20for%20all%20citizens%2C%20regardless%20of%20religious%2C%20ethnic%20and%20cultural%20identities.%20%E2%80%9CAmongst%20the%20numerous%20religious%20groups%2C%20Islam%20occupies%20a%20unique%20and%20significant%20position%20of%20pride%2C%20with%20India%20being%20home%20to%20the%20second%20largest%20Muslim%20population%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20adding%20noting%20Indian%20Muslims%20are%20equal%20in%20number%20to%20the%20cumulative%20population%20of%20more%20than%2033%20members%20of%20the%20Organisation%20of%20Islamic%20Cooperation%20(OIC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OIC%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fram-navami-violence-oic-expresses-deep-concern-india-call-statement-communal-mindset%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20concern%3C%2Fa%3E%20several%20times%20over%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmounting%20Islamophobia%20and%20systemic%20targeting%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%20India%20has%20responded%20to%20these%20concerns%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20organisation%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmanipulated%E2%80%9D%20by%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%20forces%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20euphemism%20for%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20deep%20spiritual%20content%20of%20Hinduism%20and%20Islam%20brought%20people%20together%20and%20helped%20in%20bringing%20about%20social%20and%20intellectual%20understanding%20of%20each%20other.%20It%20gave%20rise%20to%20a%20distinct%20and%20vibrant%20expression%20of%20peace%20and%20harmony%2C%E2%80%9D%20Doval%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIslam%20evolved%20into%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdistinct%20syncretic%20tradition%20that%20is%20dynamic%20and%20fluid%20and%20is%20profoundly%20ingrained%20in%20Indian%20cultural%20life%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aninews.in%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Findias-muslim-population-is-roughly-the-size-of-combined-population-of-33-oic-states-nsa-ajit-doval20230711193924%2F%5C%22%3Enews%20agency%20%3Cem%3EANI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoval%E2%80%99s%20comments%20on%20dissent%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cinfinite%20ability%E2%80%9D%20to%20absorb%20it%20were%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20a%20speech%20he%20made%20to%20graduating%20police%20officers%20in%20November%202021.%20He%20had%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhuman-rights-violations-modi-government%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20civil%20society%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfourth%20frontier%20of%20war%E2%80%9D%20which%20could%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmanipulated%20to%20hurt%20a%20nation%E2%80%99s%20interests%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Al-Issa%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20need%20to%20encourage%20diversity%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20benefit%20from%20the%20common%20values%20that%20we%20share%20and%20work%20to%20strengthen%20them.%E2%80%9D%20He%20described%20India%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CHindu-majority%20country%20with%20a%20secular%20constitution%E2%80%9D%20where%20the%20Muslim%20community%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20important%20component%20of%20society%20that%20is%20proud%20of%20its%20nationality%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20awareness%E2%80%9D%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%20should%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctool