ce%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20France%20is%20ready%20to%20roll%20out%20a%20red%20carpet%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20European%20nation%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20packed%20with%20several%20interactions%20with%20the%20top%20leadership%20in%20France%20to%20discuss%20issues%20of%20global%20interest%20that%20show%20the%20growing%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20PM%20Modi%20is%20the%20Guest%20of%20Honour%20at%20Bastille%20Day%20celebrations%20in%20France%20this%20year.%20On%20the%20occasion%2C%20the%20Tri-services%20contingent%20from%20India%20will%20participate%2C%20including%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20National%20Day%2C%20or%20Bastille%20Day%2C%20occupies%20a%20special%20place%20in%20French%20consciousness.%20This%20day%20commemorates%20the%20Storming%20of%20the%20Bastille%20Prison%20in%201789%20during%20the%20French%20Revolution.%20The%20Bastille%20Day%20Parade%20is%20the%20highlight%20of%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20Celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20uncommon%20for%20foreign%20politicians%20to%20be%20invited%20as%20the%20Guest%20of%20Honour%20for%20Bastille%20Day%20(the%20previous%20time%20was%20in%202017%20when%20the%20US%20President%20(Donald%20Trump%20at%20that%20time)%20was%20given%20the%20invitation).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipation%20by%20foreign%20marching%20bands%20and%20aircraft%20is%20even%20more%20unusual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20becomes%20all%20the%20way%20more%20important%20as%20it%20coincides%20with%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20India-France%20Strategic%20Partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20(PM%20Modi%20and%20French%20President%20Macron)%20share%20great%20personal%20chemistry%20between%20the%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20a%20special%20gesture%20by%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20is%20likely%2C%20which%20includes%20multiple%20meetings%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20PM%2C%20particularly%20a%20private%20dinner%20and%20joint%20meeting%20with%20CEOs.%20Also%2C%20a%20State%20Banquet%20at%20the%20iconic%20Louvre%20Museum%20on%20Bastille%20Day%20will%20likely%20be%20hosted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20interaction%20with%20the%20entire%20political%20leadership%20of%20France%2C%20including%20President%20Macron%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Borne%20and%20the%20Presidents%20of%20the%20Senate%20(Upper%20House)%20and%20National%20Assembly%20(Lower%20House)%20is%20also%20expected%20during%20his%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20strong%20focus%20will%20be%20laid%20on%20trade%20and%20economy%20with%20a%20CEO%20Forum%20comprising%20big%20names%20from%20the%20Indian%20and%20French%20sides.%20A%20close%20collaboration%20not%20just%20on%20bilateral%20issues%20but%20also%20on%20what%20the%20two%20countries%20can%20do%20on%20global%20issues%20will%20be%20looked%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM's%20visit%20has%20been%20preceded%20by%20numerous%20activities%20organized%20by%20our%20Embassy%2C%20including%20Namaste%20France%20earlier%20this%20week.%20Interaction%20with%20the%20prestigious%20La%20Seine%20Musicale%20with%20the%20Indian%20community%20is%20also%20expected%2C%20as%20per%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbitious%20outcomes%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20France%20visit%20are%20anticipated%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20defence%2C%20space%2C%20geostrategic%20planning%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20energy%2C%20climate%20action%2C%20museology%2C%20student%20mobility%2C%20interpersonal%20relations%2C%20sports%2C%20and%20culture%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20and%20France%20are%20celebrating%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20their%20Strategic%20Partnership%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Indian%20military%20contingent%20would%20also%20be%20part%20of%20the%20marching%20contingent%20on%20Bastille%20Day%2C%20alongside%20their%20French%20counterparts%20to%20mark%20this%20important%20milestone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20invitation%20of%20France%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20be%20the%20Guest%20of%20Honour%20on%20France's%20National%20Day%20on%20July%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20traditional%20military%20parade%20is%20held%20in%20Paris%20during%20Bastille%20Day%20on%20July%2014.%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%20will%20coincide%20with%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20partnership%26quot%3B%20between%20France%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister's%20visit%20is%20expected%20to%20herald%20the%20next%20phase%20in%20the%20India-France%20Strategic%20Partnership%20by%20setting%20new%20and%20ambitious%20goals%20for%20our%20strategic%2C%20cultural%2C%20scientific%2C%20academic%2C%20and%20economic%20cooperation%2C%20including%20in%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20industries%2C%20as%20per%20the%20official%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689091140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F0mh9uci8_pm-modi_625x300_08_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbastille-day-ceo-forum-pm-modis-packed-schedule-in-france-4198197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20France%20is%20ready%20to%20roll%20out%20a%20red%20carpet%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20European%20nation%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20packed%20with%20several%20interactions%20with%20the%20top%20leadership%20in%20France%20to%20discuss%20issues%20of%20global%20interest%20that%20show%20the%20growi%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbastille-day-ceo-forum-pm-modis-packed-schedule-i