July%204%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20violence%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20were%20reported%20from%20Imphal%20West%20and%20Imphal%20East%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20July%203%20order%2C%20which%20sought%20an%20%E2%80%98updated%20status%20report%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2010%2C%20submitted%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%2016-page%20report%20noted%20that%205%2C995%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20had%20been%20registered%20as%20of%20July%204%20and%20six%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20FIRs%E2%80%9D%20had%20been%20transferred%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20for%20investigation%20%E2%80%9Cindependently%20and%20with%20transparency%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2F142-people-killed-and-17-missing-in-manipur-violence-till-july-4-state-tells-sc%2Farticle67064032.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20still%20continues%20to%20rage%20in%20the%20state%20even%20after%20two%20months%20despite%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20stating%20that%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control.%20According%20to%20fact-finding%20teams%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2F2-months-of-manipur-riots-people-say-present-and-future-have-been-destroyed-state-has-failed-them%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20team%20of%20reporters%2C%20which%20visited%20the%20state%2C%20over%20200%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20over%2060%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20since%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%20on%20May%203.%20There%20are%20no%20signs%20of%20normalcy%20returning%2C%20as%20a%20policeman%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-policeman-killed-10-injured-in-kangpokpi-district%5C%22%3Ekilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2010%20people%20were%20injured%20in%20Phayeng%20and%20Singda%20villages%20of%20Kangpokpi%20district%20in%20fresh%20violence%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmanipur-govt-most-deaths-in-imphal-west-east-churachandpur-8825006%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20official%20report%20said%20Imphal%20West%20and%20Imphal%20East%20collectively%20accounted%20for%2058%20of%20these%20deaths%20%E2%80%93%2029%20each.%20Churachandpur%2C%20another%20worst-affected%20district%2C%20reported%2026%20deaths.%20The%20valley%20districts%20of%20Kakching%20and%20Bishnupur%20registered%2021%20deaths%20and%2018%20deaths%20respectively.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20hill%20district%20of%20Kangpokpi%20recorded%20eight%20deaths.%20The%20other%20districts%20where%20deaths%20have%20been%20recorded%20are%20Tengnoupal%20(4)%2C%20Thoubal%20(4)%2C%20Kamjong%20(2)%2C%20and%20Chandel%20(1).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20arson%2C%20it%20said%20there%20had%20been%205%2C053%20reported%20incidents%20of%20arson%20till%20July%203%2C%20of%20which%20the%20most%20were%20in%20Kangpokpi%20(1%2C091)%2C%20followed%20by%20Churachandpur%20(1%2C043).%20As%20many%20as%20938%20incidents%20of%20arson%20were%20reported%20in%20Imphal%20East%20and%20528%20in%20Bishnupur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%2054%2C488%20people%20were%20still%20living%20in%20354%20relief%20camps.%20The%20Centre%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%20said%2C%20had%20provided%20financial%20assistance%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20101%20crore%20for%20the%20management%20of%20relief%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20note%20of%20the%20status%20report%20filed%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-points-to-its-limited-role-in-quelling-manipur-violence-puts-onus-on-elected-govt%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20de-escalating%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20is%20limited%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20elected%20government%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control.%20The%20court%20was%20hearing%20two%20separate%20petitions%20filed%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Tribal%20Forum%20Delhi%20and%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Hill%20Areas%20Committee%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Legislative%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20told%20the%C2%A0petitioners%20not%20to%20use%20court%20proceedings%20to%20escalate%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20maintain%20restraint%20when%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%20alleged%20that%20Manipur%20violence%20is%20a%20case%20of%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%E2%80%9D%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESC%20dismisses%20petition%20of%20Manipur%20Tribal%20Forum%20Delhi%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20July%2011%2C%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Tribal%20Forum%20Delhi%2C%20which%20sought%20protection%20for%20the%20Kuki%20tribe%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Feast-and-northeast%2Fsc-declines-plea-filed-by-manipur-tribal-forum-seeking-protection-of-kuki-tribe-by-indian-army-1235935.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20it%20would%20not%20be%20appropriate%20to%20issue%20such%20orders%20to%20the%20Army%20and%20paramilitary%20forces.%20However%2C%20it%20said%20it%20will%20impress%20upon%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20to%20make%20arrangements%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20citizens%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFemale%20lawyer%20booked%20under%20sedition%20granted%20protection%20from%20arrest%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20granted%20interim%20protection%20from%20arrest%20to%20Deeksha%20Dwivedi%2C%20a%20lawyer%20against%20whom%20a%20case%20was%20registered%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20under%20sedition%20and%20other%20charges.%20She%20was%20part%20of%20a%20three-member%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-fir-fact-finding-team%5C%22%3Efact-finding%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20Annie%20Raja%20and%20Nisha%20Siddhu%20of%20the%20National%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Women%20(NFIW)%2C%20which%20visited%20the%20state%20to%20understand%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20concluding%20their%20visit%20to%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20they%20addressed%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20which%20they%20described%20the%20crisis%20as%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20violence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%C2%A0Justices%20P.S.%20Narasimha%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20will%20hear%20Dwivedi%E2%80%99s%20petition%20on%20July%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689081609000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F142-killed-manipur-violence-july-4-supreme-court-status-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manipur%20government%20on%20Monday%20filed%20a%20status%20report%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20giving%20its%20account%20of%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F142-killed-manipur-violence-july-4-supreme-court-status-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Heatwave%20to%20grip%20southern%20Europe%20until%20at%20least%20end%20of%20next%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689081480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F768x4