griculture-online-marketplace-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ee-commerce%20business%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20other%20states%20and%20connect%20more%20farmers%20to%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20with%20this%20motivation%20that%20Aniket%20continues%20to%20do%20the%20work%20despite%20reluctance%20from%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20are%20farmers%2C%20but%20they%20always%20wanted%20me%20to%20quit%20farming%20and%20earn%20a%20decent%20income%20in%20an%20engineering%20job%20in%20the%20city.%20I%20believe%20that%20I%20could%20have%20established%20a%20good%20career%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%2C%20where%20there%20would%20have%20been%20job%20security.%20But%20I%20am%20fortunate%20to%20pursue%20my%20passion%20and%20be%20of%20some%20help%20to%20farmers%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689080476000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faniket-gharge-4-1689076741.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D323320%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra's%20Aniket%20Gharge%20and%20Jay%20Sidhpura%20started%20the%20Indian%20Farmer%20Entrepreneurs%20(IFE)%20Store%2C%20an%20online%20marketplace%20to%20help%20farmers%20directly%20sell%20their%20produce%20and%20value-added%20products%20to%20consumers%20without%20the%20interference%20of%20middlemen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323320%2Ffriends-zero-commission-online-market-helps-farmers-double-their-income-minus-middlemen%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dalits%20in%20Telangana%20Village%20Defy%20Years%20of%20Untouchability%2C%20Reject%20Segregation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11173858%2F279289002_297672015877143_6008637976098420586_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20young%20Dalit%20men%20in%20Telangana%20defied%20years%20of%20caste%20discrimination%2C%20humiliation%20and%20social%20exclusion%20last%20week%2C%20when%20they%20insisted%20that%20their%20local%20village%20barber%20cut%20their%20hair%20in%20the%20same%20salon%20as%20everyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20their%20childhood%2C%20these%20men%20from%20Timmapur%20village%20of%20Siddipet%20district%E2%80%99s%20Jagadevpur%20mandal%20were%20denied%20entry%20into%20the%20local%20salon.%20They%20were%20forced%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20barber%E2%80%99s%20practice%20of%20cutting%20their%20hair%20under%20a%20tamarind%20tree%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20village%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20many%20forms%20of%20untouchability%20that%20continues%20to%20prevail%20across%20the%20country%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20July%205%2C%20five%20Madiga%20(Scheduled%20Caste)%20men%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20Posanpally%20Ramanujam%2C%20Gundru%20Narsimlu%2C%20Posanpally%20Murali%2C%20Posanpally%20Naveen%20and%20Gundru%20Srikanth%20%E2%80%94%20resisted%20this%20discriminatory%20practice.%20And%20when%20the%20barber%20Shyamsunder%20still%20denied%20them%20impartial%20service%2C%20they%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20local%20police%20against%20him%2C%20and%20several%20members%20of%20the%20locally%20dominant%20Mudiraj%20(Backward%20Class)%20community%20who%20had%20allegedly%20pressured%20the%20barber%20to%20deny%20fair%20service%20to%20Madigas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11175950%2Ftimmapur_barber_shop_for_Sc-colony_650.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11175950%2Ftimmapur_barber_shop_for_Sc-colony_650.jpg%20650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11175950%2Ftimmapur_barber_shop_for_Sc-colony_650-300x185.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662671%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20tree%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20village%20where%20Dalit%20men%20got%20haircuts.%20Photo%3A%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resistance%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20all%20that%20sudden.%20It%20had%20been%20building%20for%20a%20while%2C%20triggered%20by%20decades%20of%20social%20exclusion%20and%20stoked%20by%20a%20couple%20of%20recent%20incidents%20of%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20ago%20on%20June%208%2C%20Timmapur%20marked%20a%20%E2%80%98festival%20of%20lakes%E2%80%99%20as%20part%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20decennial%20celebrations%20of%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20formation.%20As%20the%20Dalit%20residents%20were%20about%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20community%20cooking%20event%2C%20members%20of%20the%20dominant%20Mudiraj%20community%20and%20other%20BC%20communities%20allegedly%20objected.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20humiliated%20us%20by%20saying%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20eat%20food%20cooked%20by%20us.%20They%20only%20wanted%20us%20to%20clean%20up%20after%20them%20by%20picking%20up%20the%20leaves%20(used%20as%20plates)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Narsimlu%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Affronted%20by%20this%2C%20Narsimlu%20(25)%20said%20that%20he%20and%20many%20other%20Dalit%20residents%20stormed%20out%20of%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20defiance%20had%20its%20repercussions.%20They%20were%20subjected%20to%20harsher%20social%20boycott%2C%20as%20people%20allegedly%20stopped%20hiring%20Madigas%20to%20play%20the%20%3Cem%3Edappu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(drum)%20at%20various%20events%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20their%20main%20sources%20of%20income.%20But%20Narsimlu%2C%20Murali%20and%20the%20others%20decided%20to%20double%20down%20and%20escalate%20their%20resistance.%20On%20July%201%2C%20around%2040%20Dalit%20men%20entered%20a%20local%20Hanuman%20temple%20where%20their%20entry%20was%20historically%20denied.%20The%20privileged%20castes%20responded%20by%20cutting%20power%20supply%20to%20the%20temple%2C%20and%20have%20now%20boycotted%20the%20temple%20too%2C%20another%20Dalit%20resident%20Posanpally%20Raju%20(30)%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11180207%2Ftimmapur_hanuman_Temple_650.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11180207%2Ftimmapur_hanuman_Temple_650.jpg%20650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11180207%2Ftimmapur_hanuman_Temple_650-300x185.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662672%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDalit%20men%20at%20Timarpur%E2%80%99s%20Hanuman%20temple%20where%20they%20have%20been%20historically%20denied%20entry.%20Photo%3A%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAll%20of%20these%20hostilities%20culminated%20in%20the%20July%205%20incident%2C%20when%20the%20five%20men%20confronted%20the%20barber%20Shyamsunder%20and%20demanded%20services%20inside%20his%20salon%20alongside%20the%20other%20residents%20of%20the%20village.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNtvTeluguLive%2Fstatus%2F1676843538271592451%5C%22%3EVisuals%20of%20the%20confrontation%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0showed%20the%20barber%20refusing%20service%2C%20following%20which%20the%20men%20lodged%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20him%20and%20seven%20elders%20of%20the%20Mudiraj%20community%20(including%20a%20village%20leader%20affiliated%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20Nayini%20Mahender)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20two%20members%20of%20the%20Rajaka%20(BC)%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Jagadevpur%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20caste%20discrimination%20under%20section%203(1)(v)%20of%20the%20The%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%20Gajwel%E2%80%99s%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(ACP)%20M.%20Ramesh%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3EBarbershop%20on%20the%20peripheries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-attr%3D%5C%22not-done%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-google-query-id%3D%5C%22CPL8sZfKhoADFSSqZgIdVqgKNw%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20around%20500%20members%20of%20the%20Madiga%20community%20%E2%80%94%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20disadvantaged%20among%20SCs%20%E2%80%94%20living%20in%20Timmapur%20village%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Gajwel%20constituency%20represented%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao.%20The%20Mudiraj%20(BC)%20community%20is%20the%20most%20dominant%20in%20the%20village%2C%20followed%20by%20Gollas%20(a%20pastoral%20community)%2C%20Padmashalis%20(whose%20traditional%20occupation%20is%20weaving)%2C%20and%20Rajakas%20(whose%20traditional%20occupation%20is%20washing%20clothes)%2C%20all%20categorised%20as%20BCs.%20The%20barber%2C%20Shyamsunder%2C%20belongs%20to%20the%20Nayee%20Brahmin%20community%2C%20also%20categorised%20as%20BC%20but%20less%20powerful%20than%20Mudirajs.%20Nayee%20Brahmins%20themselves%20are%20often%20subject%20to%20caste%20discrimination%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-google-query-id%3D%5C%22CPL8sZfKhoADFSSqZgIdVqgKNw%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20residents%20of%20Timmapur%E2%80%99s%20Dalit%20colony%2C%20Shyamsunder%E2%80%99s%20barbershop%20is%20situated%20among%20the%20houses%20of%20the%20BC%20residents%20of%20various%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20Friday%2C%20the%20barber%20shuts%20that%20salon%2C%20and%20provides%20services%20to%20Dalits%20under%20a%20tamarind%20tree%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Raju.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-google-query-id%3D%5C%22CPL8sZfKhoADFSSqZgIdVqgKNw%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fdalits-telangana-village-defy-years-untouchability-reject-segregated-barbershops-179544%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-google-query-id%3D%5C%22CPL8sZfKhoADFSSqZgIdVqgKNw%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDecades%20of%20ostracism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20childhood%20days%2C%20Raju%20remembers%20classmates%20from%20privileged%20castes%20bullying%20him%20and%20his%20friends%20in%20the%20name%20of%20their%20caste.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20we%20were%20friends%20with%20classmates%20from%20privileged%20castes%2C%20they%20never%20allowed%20us%20inside%20their%20homes.%20We%20were%20never%20allowed%20to%20eat%20with%20them%20either%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20There%E2%80%99s%20one%20major%20incident%20he%20vividly%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202003%2C%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Class%206%2C%20I%20entered%20the%20local%20Hanuman%20temple%20along%20with%20a%20few%20other%20boys%20of%20my%20age%20from%20my%20colony%2C%20though%20we%20knew%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20allowed.%20For%20nearly%20six%20years%20after%20that%2C%20the%20temple%20remained%20closed%2C%20and%20no%20one%20in%20the%20village%20hired%20people%20from%20our%20colony%20to%20play%20the%20dappu%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20After%20this%2C%20Raju%20and%20three%20other%20boys%20from%20the%20village%20left%20for%20Gajwel%20town%20to%20study%20in%20a%20government%20residential%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20now%20has%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20and%20works%20for%20a%20private%20firm.%20Three%20of%20the%20nearly%2040%20young%20Dalit%20men%20in%20the%20village%20have%20attended%20college%2C%20all%20first-generation%20graduates.%20A%20few%20others%20had%20to%20stop%20their%20formal%20education%20after%20Class%2012.%20Narsaiah%2C%20a%2045-year-old%20Dalit%20farmer%20from%20the%20village%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20generation%20is%20used%20to%20such%20%5Bdiscriminatory%5D%20customs%2C%20but%20these%20young%20men%20are%20educated.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20tolerate%20disrespect%20anymore%20and%20want%20things%20to%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11175741%2Fmain_timmapur_1200_0.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11175741%2Fmain_timmapur_1200_0.jpg%20750w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11175741%2Fmain_timmapur_1200_0-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662670%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDalit%20men%20defying%20social%20exclusion%20in%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Timarpur%20village.%20Photo%3A%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarsimulu%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20as%20a%20driver%20after%20finishing%20Class%2012%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAttending%20events%20held%20by%20anti-caste%20organisations%20and%20following%20discussions%20of%20anti-caste%20leaders%20on%20YouTube%20have%20helped%20us%20become%20more%20aware%20of%20our%20rights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%2C%20who%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20college%20graduates%20from%20the%20colony%2C%20said%20he%20was%20active%20in%20student%20politics%20in%20his%20college%20days.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20telling%20the%20youth%20in%20our%20colony%20that%20we%20should%20stop%20normalising%20casteist%20practices%20in%20our%20village.%20It%20was%20difficult%20to%20convince%20them%20at%20first%20and%20I%20gave%20up.%20But%20the%20incident%20at%20the%20lake%20festival%20had%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20others.%20They%20themselves%20approached%20me%20and%20asked%20if%20we%20should%20resist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20village%20lake%20festival%20in%20June%2C%20when%20the%20privileged%20castes%20refused%20to%20eat%20food%20cooked%20by%20Dalits%2C%20the%20younger%20generation%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20firm%20stand%2C%20and%20walked%20away.%20When%20they%20faced%20retaliation%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20more%20severe%20boycott%2C%20Raju%2C%20Narsimlu%2C%20Murali%20and%20the%20others%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20struggle%20back%20to%20the%20Hanuman%20temple%20some%20of%20them%20remembered%20entering%20as%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20decades%20after%20his%20childhood%20incident%2C%20Raju%20entered%20the%20Hanuman%20temple%20once%20again%20on%20July%201%20along%20with%20Narsimlu%20and%20others.%20He%20alleged%20that%20after%20their%20entry%2C%20the%20power%20supply%20to%20the%20temple%20was%20discontinued.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BC%20communities%20do%20not%20want%20to%20enter%20the%20temple%20anymore.%20They%E2%80%99re%20saying%20they%E2%80%99ll%20build%20a%20new%20Hanuman%20temple%20for%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raju%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%2C%20on%20July%205%2C%20Raju%2C%20Narsimlu%2C%20Murali%2C%20Naveen%20and%20Srikanth%20decided%20to%20oppose%20the%20segregated%20barbershop%20system.%20When%20they%20went%20to%20Shyamsunder%E2%80%99s%20salon%2C%20the%20barber%20declined%20services%20citing%20instructions%20from%20caste%20elders%20of%20the%20Mudiraj%20and%20Rajaka%20communities%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20police%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20an%20act%20of%20assertion%2C%20after%20experiencing%20repeated%20social%20boycotts%20in%20the%20village%20for%20decades%E2%80%9D%2C%20national%20secretary%20of%20Dalit%20Bahujan%20Front%20(DBF)%20P%20Shankar%20told%20TNM.%20After%20the%20incident%2C%20Shankar%20and%20other%20anti-caste%20activists%20staged%20a%20demonstration%20at%20the%20Jagdevpur%20mandal%20revenue%20office%20demanding%20strict%20punishment%20for%20those%20practising%20untouchability%20towards%20Dalits%20in%20Timmapur.%20Shankar%20demanded%20that%20the%20Siddipet%20district%20Collector%20and%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20must%20visit%20the%20village%20and%20facilitate%20Dalits%E2%80%99%20entry%20into%20the%20temple%2C%20barbershop%20and%20other%20public%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShankar%20said%20that%20the%20BC%20communities%20who%20hold%20power%20in%20the%20village%20are%20both%20politically%20and%20numerically%20dominant.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20these%20communities%20don%E2%80%99t%20face%20untouchability%20themselves%2C%20they%20use%20their%20relatively%20advantaged%20position%20to%20dominate%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20observing%20that%20there%20was%20a%20rising%20trend%20of%20attacks%20on%20Dalits%20by%20BCs%20in%20Telangana%20while%20listing%20a%20few%20recent%20atrocities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20a%20Dalit%20man%20named%20Shyamalapalli%20Yellaiah%20and%20his%20son%20Shekar%20were%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fmurder-dalit-father-and-son-sparks-tension-telangana-s-rajanna-sircilla-district-82973%5C%22%3Ebrutally%20hacked%20to%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0over%20a%20land%20dispute%20allegedly%20by%20three%20persons%20from%20the%20Mudiraj%20community%2C%20in%20Rajanna%20Sircilla%20district%20neighbouring%20Siddipet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20district%2C%20over%20200%20Mudiraj%20men%20and%20women%20from%20the%20same%20Mudi