s-sc%5C%22%3Eaffidavit%20sings%20praises%20of%20how%20much%20betterment%20has%20been%20brought%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20after%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20attempt%20thus%20to%20shift%20goal%20post%20from%20the%20legal%2Fconstitutional%20aspect%20of%20the%20matter%20to%20an%20administrative%2Fpolitical%20one%20seems%20a%20dead%20giveaway%20of%20how%20weak%20it%20knows%20itself%20to%20be%20on%20the%20constitutional%20aspect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20most%20heartening%20that%20the%20honourable%20judges%20on%20the%20constitution%20bench%20have%20instantly%20pronounced%20on%20the%20irrelevance%20of%20the%20new%20affidavit%2C%20affirming%20that%20issues%20related%20to%20how%20conditions%20in%20the%20state%20were%20before%20and%20are%20claimed%20to%20be%20after%20the%20abrogation%20are%20redundant%20matters%20to%20the%20challenges%20made%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20fraught%20decision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20its%20concern%20is%20in%20toto%20with%20determining%20whether%20what%20the%20Modi%20government%20did%20on%20August%205%2C2019%20was%20constitutionally%20tenable%20or%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20determined%20to%20take%20up%20the%20case%20after%20an%20interregnum%20of%20some%20four%20years%20may%20also%20be%20suggestive%20of%20the%20merit%20in%20the%20challenges%20made%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20contested%2Fcontroversial%20decision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20also%20the%20fact%20that%20over%20these%20years%20the%20Modi%20government%20made%20no%20move%20to%20persuade%20the%20top%20court%20to%20take%20up%20the%20matter%20for%20quick%20disposal%20%E2%80%93%20something%20this%20government%20would%20surely%20have%20chosen%20to%20do%20had%20it%20been%20certain%20of%20