the%20erstwhile%20case%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsupreme-court-ayodhya-babri-masjid-ram-janambhoomi%5C%22%3EBabri%20Masjid-Ram%20temple%20title%20dispute.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20that%20matter%2C%20we%20recall%2C%20the%20honourable%20court%2C%20after%20laying%20down%20that%20the%20demolished%20structure%20had%20indeed%20been%20a%20mosque%2C%20that%20induction%20of%20idols%20into%20its%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20was%20an%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdesecration%2C%E2%80%9D%20that%20demolishing%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccriminal%E2%80%9D%20act%2C%20determined%20to%20award%20the%20site%20to%20the%20litigants%20who%20believed%20a%20temple%20to%20Lord%20Ram%20had%20to%20be%20built%20on%20that%20very%20spot.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20court%20of%20course%20cited%20due%20powers%20vested%20in%20it%20to%20make%20such%20a%20determination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20forthcoming%20decision%20on%20challenges%20to%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20will%20not%20but%20be%20of%20the%20greatest%20import%20in%20shaping%20the%20future%20both%20of%20the%20present%20Union%20Territory%20and%20of%20national%20politics%20overall%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come%20goes%20without%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbadri-raina%5C%22%3EBadri%20Raina%3C%2Fa%3E%20taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689074178000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F05154349%2FSrinagar-article-370-security-curfew2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000095B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-narendra-modi-article-370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20its%20concern%20is%20in%20toto%20with%20determining%20whether%20what%20the%20Modi%20government%20did%