k%20illegal%20influx%20from%20Myanmar%20into%20India%E2%80%9D.%20It%20also%20added%20that%20state%20governments%20have%20no%20powers%20to%20grant%20%E2%80%9Crefugee%E2%80%9D%20status%20to%20%E2%80%9Cany%20foreigner%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20India%20is%20not%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Refugee%20Convention%20of%201951%20and%20its%201967%20Protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20had%20on%20June%2030%20blamed%20illegal%20migrants%20from%20Myanmar%20for%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20analysis%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%20%C2%A0Sangeeta%20Barooah%20Pisharoty%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fneighbouring-manipur-violence-myanmar%5C%22%3Eillustrated%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20border%20troubles%20have%20always%20dictated%20domestic%20politics%20in%20the%20northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689058030000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmha-pushes-manipur-mizoram-to-record-biometric-details-of-illegal-migrants%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20had%20earlier%20blamed%20illegal%20migrants%20from%20Myanmar%20for%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmha-pushes-manipur-mizoram-to-record-biometric-details-of-illegal-migrants%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ozempic%20and%20Saxenda%20under%20investigation%20in%20EU%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689057960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F22%2F12%2F70x70%2Fskynews-ozempic-drug_6007822.jpg%3F20221228141017%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnovo-nordisk-stock-value-drops-a