Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20birth%20of%20Aazol%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApurva%20decided%20to%20take%20early%20retirement%20in%202021%20to%20brainstorm%20ideas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20spoke%20to%20my%20son%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20he%20is%20also%20passionate%20about%20helping%20the%20bottom%20tier%20of%20society.%20This%20was%20it%3B%20we%20both%20made%20up%20our%20minds%20to%20find%20a%20way%20of%20helping%20the%20underprivileged%20by%20giving%20them%20a%20livelihood%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20year%2C%20Apurva%20and%20Siddharth%20went%20to%20Mahalaxmi%20Saras%20Exhibition%20which%20happens%20every%20year%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20exhibition%20is%20by%20people%20from%20all%20across%20Maharashtra%20from%20various%20SHGs%20showcasing%20and%20selling%20their%20produce.%20While%20chatting%20with%20these%20women%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20they%20did%20not%20have%20many%20avenues%20to%20sell%20these%20products.%20There%20were%20so%20many%20snacks%20and%20products%20like%20chutney%2C%20sauces%20and%20syrups%20that%20I%20had%20never%20seen%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20lived%20in%20Maharashtra%20my%20whole%20life%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20see%20so%20many%20snacks%20that%20nobody%20knew%20about.%20Additionally%2C%20all%20these%20were%20handmade%20and%20without%20preservatives.%20Those%20women%20also%20told%20me%20how%20they%20do%20not%20have%20much%20employment%20and%20were%20constantly%20under%20financial%20stress%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20conversations%20with%20the%20women%20gave%20the%20duo%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20company%20that%20could%20bridge%20this%20gap.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20create%20a%20marketplace%20and%20supply%20chain%20for%20these%20women%3F%E2%80%99%20and%20then%20in%20September%202021%2C%20Aazol%20was%20born%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp