ividual%20flat%20owners%2C%20but%20we%20can%20set%20up%20such%20a%20system%20for%20an%20entire%20building%2C%20as%20it%20would%20not%20be%20cost-effective%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20residential%20complexes%2C%20Abhijit%20aims%20to%20expand%20this%20system%20into%20restaurants%2C%20institutes%2C%20canteens%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20are%20totally%20dependent%20on%20the%20monsoon%20every%20year%2C%20which%20has%20not%20failed%20us.%20But%20with%20changing%20weather%20patterns%20amid%20climate%20change%2C%20we%20are%20to%20get%20below%20average%20monsoon%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20Our%20water%20resource%20is%20limited%20but%20our%20consumption%20is%20increasing%2C%20which%20is%20not%20sustainable%20unless%20we%20take%20such%20initiatives.%20Hopefully%2C%20with%20our%20low-cost%20recycling%20system%2C%20people%20will%20come%20forward%20to%20adopt%20such%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1808621%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUnion%20Jal%20Shakti%20Minister%20Launches%20Sujlam%202.0%20Campaign%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EPublished%20by%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20on%2023%20March%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Abhijit%20Sathe%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688563709000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1688562544.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D322812%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pune%E2%80%99s%20Abhijit%20Sathe%20started%20JalSevak%20Solutions%20to%20provide%20an%20affordable%20alternative%20to%20greywater%20recycling%20to%20Indian%20households.%20He%20has%20helped%20install%20this%20compact%20system%20in%20r