e%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%20June%202021%2C%20Project%20Surya%20is%20a%20social%20initiative%20to%20create%20awareness%20and%20provide%20assistance%20to%20children%20living%20with%20Type%201%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20%3Cem%3EICMR%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%20released%20in%202022%2C%20India%20has%20nearly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F299477%2Fhealth-benefits-of-spine-gourd-for-managing-diabetes-boosting-immunity-food-science%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E95%2C600%20cases%20of%20Type%201%20diabetes%3C%2Fa%3E%20below%2014%20years%20of%20age%2C%20and%2015%2C900%20cases%20are%20diagnosed%20each%20year%20in%20this%20age%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndividuals%20with%20Type%201%20diabetes%20need%20support%20to%20survive%2C%20using%20insulin%20and%20other%20therapies%2C%20and%20to%20live%20their%20entire%20life%20without%20stigma%2C%20restrictions%2C%20or%20disabling%20complications%20due%20to%20their%20illness.%20In%20India%2C%20there%20exists%20considerable%20variability%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20diabetes%20care%2C%20which%20depends%20upon%20various%20factors%20such%20as%20accessibility%20to%20services%2C%20affordability%20of%20drugs%2C%20attitude%20and%20perceptions%20of%20care%20providers%2C%20lack%20of%20specialists%20and%20diabetes%20educators%2C%20standardised%20laboratories%20and%20treatment%20guidelines.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20this%20gap%20in%20quality%20of%20care%2C%20along%20with%20mental%20health%20support%2C%20that%20Divaa%20seeks%20to%20provide%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20through%20her%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201036px)%20100vw%2C%201036px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa3-1688532225.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221036%5C%22%20alt%